Weidos ESP32 package 2.0.0  2024.01.29

Improvements
* Added extraflag NBIOT
* Define SARA_R412 pins in pins_weidos file
* Change core hardwareserial functions to virtual
* Added Library for NB-IOT board
* Udate HardwareSerialPIC library with bugfixes

Bugfixes
* HardwareSerialPIC lose of data  


New Boards & updates
* Weidos-ESP32-NBIOT-A1 board


