Weidos ESP32 package 1.0.1  2022.12.19

Improvements
* Analog output pin AO_0 initialized to 0V by default.


Bugfixes
* Internal identifier name changed to avoid multidefinition with external libraries.


New Boards & updates
* Weidos-ESP32-LoRa-A1 board


Weidos ESP32 package 1.0.0  2022.09.13

* First public release.

